    <summary>CLI wrapper for Wheels MVC framework - A convenient wrapper for the Wheels CommandBox CLI</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
The Wheels CLI provides a convenient wrapper for the Wheels CommandBox CLI tools.

Instead of typing `box wheels generate model User`, you can simply type `wheels generate model User`.

This package installs a `wheels` command that passes all arguments to the underlying `box wheels` command.

## Prerequisites
- CommandBox must be installed and available in your PATH
- CommandBox can be installed from https://www.ortussolutions.com/products/commandbox

## Usage
After installation, you can use commands like:
- `wheels generate model User`
- `wheels migrate up`
- `wheels server start`
- `wheels --help`

All arguments are passed through to the underlying `box wheels` command.
]]></description>
